The uniqueness of the personal data store online is that it is completely at the user's option who can have access to what kind of information.
The company calls it "personal possession through data."
The idea for Inrupt, according to John Bruce, CEO of the company, is to provide adequate resources, processes and skills to make Solid accessible to all.
